data.description: Pristinely maintained with craftsman finishes.. This Forrester Plan is 2644 sq ft situated on a fenced in lake homesite. This home finished with hardi-plank exterior and offers 5 beds and 3 baths with a gas, tankless hot water heater, Granite counter tops, and Hardwood floors throughout. Tile in the Bathrooms and Laundry. The home has an owner suite in the back of the home away from the rest of the bedrooms. The Kitchen offers an oversized Island great for entertaining, that overlooks the lake and living room. The home is very well laid out offering a Huge Bonus Room. This one owner home has had extensive upgrades done.Including a new custom bath down stair. A beautiful outdoor space with a built-in Fire pit and grill area and Lighting. The owner also has added shiplap in various areas throughout the main floor and stairs.
